<br>
This method allows me to continuously pull, and I slowly lose mana doing it.  After about 10-12 shrooms, I may need to cannipet back to full from about 50% mana or so.<br>
<br>
Note that I'm not using KEI, do not have Improved Reclaim, have no clicky items other than a White Ceramic Band, and I'm averaging about 1.5 yellows of AA xp per hour.  If I had a clicky nuke item or KEI, I could kill faster.  If I had Improved Reclaim, this method would be awesome. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jochangaladar>Jochan Galadar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 823<br> <font color=#333333>(12/31/02 12:09:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=422.topic&index=45>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Level 60</span><hr size=1> /cheer Eloina  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=denaeb2>Denaeb2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 144<br> <font color=#333333>(1/3/03 4:15:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=422.topic&index=46>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Level 60</span><hr size=1> My approach since i hate soloing as a magician was I got to level 61 and then got enough exp in to eat some unrezzed deaths if I had too and got tagged to go to PoV/PoS now I have to say that PoV grouping exp is way fast, Some groups I can get 1 yellow aa in about 30 mins and a full aa in about 2 and a half hours. If you get to 61 Id suggest start working on trials and since your a Magician you will have ver